decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Priscilla-Presley.-CREDIT_-VALERY-HACHE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Priscilla-Presley">普里西拉·普雷斯利（Priscilla Presley）</a>赢得了她针对旧商业伙伴提起的老年虐待诉讼的第一轮。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/sofia-coppola-elvis-presley-priscilla-villain-3565087"><b>索非亚·科波拉（Sofia Coppola</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>周四（4月3日），一名洛杉矶县法官与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利（Elvis Presley）</a>的前妻子一起支持，并裁定加利福尼亚是审理诉讼的最佳场所，该场所声称她的前任企业使她从100万美元中占据了她的意愿。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priscilla-presley-to-sue-con-artist-and-old-business-associates-over-abhorrent-plan-to-drain-her-of-every-last-penny-she-had-3776955">去年7月提出的投诉</a>指控佛罗里达的纪念物拍卖师布里吉特·克鲁斯（Brigitte Kruse）以及凯文·菲亚尔科（Kevin Fialko），瓦赫·西斯莱恩（Vahe Sislyan）和林恩·沃克·赖特（Lynn Walker Wright）歪曲了她说服她赋予他们对她的权力，然后滥用她的控制权，以努力窃取她的钱。</p><p>该案现在将在几周内进行下一次听证会。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/priscilla-presley-elder-abuse-lawsuit-memorabilia-dealer-1235310991/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>的情况下，克鲁斯的丈夫克鲁斯（Kruse）和费尔科（Fialko）驳回了克鲁斯（Kruse）法官，他们说普雷斯利（Presley）对他们的虐待老年人要求在佛罗里达州对她提起合同诉讼的同时，应搁置。</p><p>被告辩称，同时在佛罗里达州对普雷斯利提起的索赔的同时，在加利福尼亚进行诉讼将“异常不便”。</p><p>爱泼斯坦说，他考虑了这一论点：“似乎是一系列永无止境的动议……将此案件移出加利福尼亚并进入佛罗里达州。”他还拒绝了普雷斯利（Presley）签署同意在佛罗里达州诉讼的合同的说法。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776969" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776969" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776969" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing.jpg" alt="Priscilla Presley le 9月4日2023  -  VENISE。 （laurent Koffel/Gamma-rapho摄影图片）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776969" class="wp-caption-text"> Priscilla Presley le 9月4日2023  -  VENISE。 （laurent Koffel/Gamma-rapho摄影图片）</figcaption></figure><p>爱泼斯坦在裁决中写道：“这并不是真正的基于合同的案件；这是一个欺诈案。” “原告正在起诉这些被告欺诈和虐待老人，据称这一方面首先使她签署了这些协议。”</p><p>他接着说，当克鲁斯，她的丈夫和费尔科可能居住在佛罗里达州和田纳西州时，普雷斯利和她所谓的证人在加利福尼亚。他还指出，据称虐待发生在加利福尼亚州，使该州“对此案具有强烈的公共利益”。</p><p>他写道：“被告似乎几乎忽略了老年人虐待指控，这不是佛罗里达州行动的一部分。但这是加利福尼亚案件的跳动。” “原告[普雷斯利]建议，对老年人的证人，对原告的影响以及原告在涉嫌行动之前和之后的情况而不是在佛罗里达州。</p><p>被告声称，普雷斯利愿意与他们达成协议，以租赁佛罗里达州的财产，并移交其宣传权的控制权。</p><p>最初的文件将克鲁斯描述为“伴侣和病态的骗子”，据称他从普雷斯利偷走了超过100万美元，并声称她“欺骗了”普雷斯利签署了签署合同，该合同使被告在诉讼中的收入为80％。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776971" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776971" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776971" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing.jpg" alt="普里西拉·普雷斯利（Priscilla Presley）于2024年2月7日在奥地利维也纳举行新闻发布会时挥手，在那里她将在今年的维也纳州歌剧院（Vienna State Opera）的歌剧院成为荣誉嘉宾。 （Alex Halada / AFP摄" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-presley-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776971" class="wp-caption-text">普里西拉·普雷斯利（Priscilla Presley）于2024年2月7日在奥地利维也纳举行新闻发布会时挥手，在那里她将在今年的维也纳州歌剧院（Vienna State Opera）的歌剧院成为荣誉嘉宾。 （Alex Halada / AFP摄</figcaption></figure><p>据称，这包括她从索非亚·科波拉（Sofia Coppola）的电影改编的《传记猫王》 <em>（Elvis）和我的电影改编的50万美元，以及</em>她与“ Cilla”化妆品交易有关的349,900美元。普雷斯利（Presley）声称，在克鲁斯（Kruse）和费尔科（Fialko）“甚至参与事务”之前，她在一家前任公司的领导下就科普拉（Coppola）的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/priscilla"><em>（Priscilla</em></a> ）进行了交易，但根据诉讼，两人“从未付给她一毛钱”。</p><p>投诉继续声称，克鲁斯（Kruse）迫使普雷斯利（Presley）“成为一种契约的奴役形式，在那里她被迫工作，以便他们可以在将来能够获得的任何收入中获得狮子的份额，”（每个<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/priscilla-presley-lawsuit-financial-elder-abuse-1235063496/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>）。</p><p> According to <a href="https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/priscilla-presley-sues-alleged-con-artist-for-seven-figure-sum/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Far Out Magazine</em></a> , the 45-page complaint saw Presley claim that Kruse had “quickly immersed herself in Presley&#39;s life” following their initial meeting in 2021. The complaint further alleged that Kruse would send “her multiple text messages a day, and telling her how much she loved her and admired her.”</p><p> Presley also alleged that Kruse and Fialko “attempted to obtain an invitation to the premiere of Priscilla at the Venice Film Festival” even though they “had absolutely nothing to do with the film.”</p><p> The complaint also alleged that Kruse and her associates were attempting to turn Presley against her previous advisors and made up false reasons for “massive payments they made to themselves from Presley&#39;s bank accounts.” </p><figure id="attachment_3776970" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776970" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776970" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1.jpg" alt="Priscilla Presley attends the Songwriters Hall of Fame 2024 induction and awards gala at the New York Marriott Marquis Hotel in New York City on June 13, 2024. (Photo by ANGELA WEISS / AFP) / ALTERNATE CROP (Photo by ANGELA WEISS/AFP via Getty Images)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Priscilla-Presley-posing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776970" class="wp-caption-text"> Priscilla Presley attends the Songwriters Hall of Fame 2024 induction and awards gala at the New York Marriott Marquis Hotel in New York City on June 13, 2024. (Photo by ANGELA WEISS / AFP) / ALTERNATE CROP (Photo by ANGELA WEISS/AFP via Getty Images)</figcaption></figure><p> Kruse and Presley have been in a legal battle for some time now with the memorabilia auctioneer previously suing Presley for breach of contract in Florida after claiming that she had walked away from their business partnership following the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lisa-marie-presley-singer-elvis-only-child-dead-aged-54-3379880">passing of her daughter Lisa Marie Presley in 2023</a> .</p><p> The new suit claimed that Kruse&#39;s previous complaint was in attempt to further control Presley and the narrative of this story. “When it became clear to the defendants that their scheme had been uncovered, they attempted to falsely portray themselves as the victims by filing a lawsuit against Presley in Florida in the name of several of the sham companies they established,” the new complaint states.</p><p> Presley is seeking at least $1 million in general damages as well as punitive damages and attorney&#39;s fees. She also seeks to have the “fraudulently-induced agreements” with the defendants rescinded in effort to regain control of her accounts.</p><p> “What Presley cannot accomplish through this action, however, is the rehabilitation of her personal friendships and relationships that were disrupted and/or materially harmed by the selfish, fraudulent acts of defendants, which could take years to accomplish, if at all,” stated the filing.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priscilla-presley-wins-round-in-elder-abuse-lawsuit-against-old-business-associates-3852137">Priscilla Presley wins round in elder abuse lawsuit against old business associates</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
